rows.label: tlk4170042104_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, Superbia... Like a scorching
flame... Like a sharp spear...

rows.label: tlk4170042104_msg0002
rows.name:
I was writing a poem about the nature
of Gula when some soldiers told me to
make it one that praises Superbia...

rows.label: tlk4170042104_msg0003
rows.name:
They said they would give me
money if I wrote a good poem,
so I will do my best!
